Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that sweaty time of year again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too hyper, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come over to your place today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just really worried you'll build\Nmore of Uzaki Hills without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I so won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy old tower.\NLooks like an evil emperor's hangout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil emperor's hangout? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my dream house,\Nstuffed full of my perfect ideals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd set up a lava trap at your own house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That {\i0}is so you can always come by and visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you want to trap me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap you? Why, I never! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the lava! What else could I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:26.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uzaki-{\i1}chan {\i0}Wants to Hang Out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:47.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Episode 5: I Want to Meddle\Nin My Friend's Business!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out there, kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rescue you.\NStay right there and be a good kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream? I was... dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've nodded off, then woke up in a panic.\NThat hasn't happened in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone saw that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be her--and only\Nat the worst possible times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around! We're in the middle of class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Senpai, Senpai, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you dreaming of falling from a high place?\NYou totally jolted awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be nodding off, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I was a witness to the big moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God{\i0}, you bug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet. Class has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoopsie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with dream interpretation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It holds that the content of\None's dreams reveal one's mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams of falling from a height, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,indicate deep-seated feelings of anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while vague unease about\None's career or personal prospects...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're anxious, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:36.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry--you can tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of falling when one is in\Nhigh spirits or getting carried away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can also be interpreted as a warning\Nto put one's feet on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting carried away there, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut {\i1}up{\i0}, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a subconscious dissatisfaction\Nwith the action or attitude responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit getting so excited!\NGet those feet on the {\i1}ground{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a timely lecture! Too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really laid bare your deepest psyche, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it. Besides, I'm not a kid--\NI don't believe in that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it {\i1}was {\i0}a little juvenile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}I'm {\i0}more of a believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychological tests, blood-type fortunes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superstition, all of it.\NThat's not what psychology is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you {\i1}say {\i0}that, but are you\Nsure you're not just acting tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But psychologically speaking--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh... I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! What are you doing, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch, Senpai. That was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when\Nyou're focused on riling someone up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of watching your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who trip down stairs\Ncan develop climacophobia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fear of descending stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what? Where'd this\Ncome from all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a psychological aftershock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also known as "the stair yips."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're navigating stairs as usual, until one day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just can't go down them smoothly,\Nor you tumble down them--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until at last, you're scared\Nof the very stairs themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I have plans with {\i1}that {\i0}guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You showed up at the perfect time, Sak.\NThose girls are {\i1}relentless{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives, Itsuhito? You running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Itsuhito Sakaki, 21 - College Junior"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's honestly not much fun going drinking\Nwith that bunch. We just don't click.{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people drink way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\i0}prefer a more stylish approach\Nto enjoying alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, sober me is left\Nto clean up the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not into that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There goes Sakaki. Aren't we going after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... But that other guy's a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah--the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are together a lot. Are they friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it feels like I barely saw\Nyou around at all last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I popped over to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okinawa?! It's not even summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had this sudden urge\Nto see that gorgeous ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's {\i0}living free and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Sak?\NAnything happen while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... hmm... What even {\i1}was {\i0}that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My days were... hard to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was ordinary enough, generally speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to classes,\Nworked my job, played games and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kept pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Will you go hog wild just {\i1}once{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hanging out with you\Nfor three years. Your life is {\i1}dull{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's depressing just hearing about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only four years of college,\Nand you're wasting it! {\i1}Enjoy {\i0}it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--? You gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Jerks like you\Nwho waste their youth are insufferable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There {\i0}you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might this person be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait--could he be--your... friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:09:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you... you really {\i1}did {\i0}have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did talk him up sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I thought he was imaginary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw me eating with him in the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you were\Npretending he was your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy... Oh, I really am so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait--you were seriously worried about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit looking at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. You're that girl\Nwho's with Sak now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a junior, like him. Name's Sakaki--pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Uzaki, sophomore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai is a hardcore gloomlord,\Nbut I hope you'll get along well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who even {\i1}are {\i0}you to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, Senpai--\NI'll still keep hanging out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where are we going to go after class today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that like\Nmy schedule's already booked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I was going\Nto hang out at your place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come over again today? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:10:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you're always hanging out\Nwith your one male friend, people'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll make fanart outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you worried about?\NDo you even know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't assume, amid all this nonsense,\Nthat I only have one male friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now--you don't have to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}that's {\i0}how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really--it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! Well, I've got another class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry; I get it. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've found love at long last!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be bashful!\NI'm your wingman--I've got your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Another giant pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of situation are you after?\NRomantic? Erotic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:49.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Summer Romance Watermelon"\N"Icy Cold" "Icy Cold" "Icy Cold"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is going to be one fun summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how long have you known each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was my junior in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. A pretty long time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how far have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any fooling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy looks good,\Nbut he's really just the worst, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is that a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you talk about--and\Nwe wouldn't tell you even if we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh... never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Eh? N-Now hang on a sec--\NI seriously don't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's fine. I mean, it's just between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know,\Nthen it doesn't count. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is {\i1}not {\i0}okay! Tell me! What did I do? Where? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Shut up! This is sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're mad at me, and I don't even know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki, too, going all in\Non the sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sexual... harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From where I stand, he's the\Nsafest creature in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it like that...\Nit's actually pretty awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, sorry. I'd just never heard\Nany romantic tales about Sak before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Mr. Serious here with\Na girl piqued my interest, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't really help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a gloomy klutz of a sleepyhead\Nvillain loner, so I keep him company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a gloomy klutz\Nof a sleepyhead villain loner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to spend my time quietly, by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two get along amazingly well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just me. I bet everyone thinks so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know: "Oh, those two must be dating."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard that tons of times?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're not--for now. I get that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're gonna have to eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's grab some ice cream\Nfrom the convenience store. My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they just run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that's not the reaction I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pictured something a little more innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not that he simply {\i1}dislikes {\i0}her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami Asai, senior. Friend of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakaki--same year as Sakurai.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}was {\i0}it? Just a friendly chat, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening in?\NYou should have joined us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teasing those two is one thing,\Nbut do you have to be so blunt about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just putting out some feelers.\NI got shut out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch over those two--and\NI won't let anyone get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing things your way may very well\Nend up nipping their love in the bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must watch them from a distance,\Nwith no unnecessary prying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're rooting for them, too, huh?\NAnd you really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed my mind.\NAfter all, we both want them to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we team up, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do {\i1}anything {\i0}for those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anyone's help! Quit your meddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what part of me wanting to observe\Nfrom out here do you not understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty crass yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you meddle\Nindiscriminately in their business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}both {\i0}are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to share, Senpai? C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want any?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. After all, you bought 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That refreshing green-blue\Npackaging... choco-mint, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is choco-mint any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choco-mint is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choco-mint...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But choco-mint--isn't that toothpaste?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look me in the eye and say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... I was wondering\Nif choco-mint was really any good,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since that's what toothpaste tastes like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is {\i1}always {\i0}what people\Nwho {\i1}don't {\i0}eat choco-mint say
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when they're mocking choco-mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mocking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0}! It started when\Nyou compared it to toothpaste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's your garbage palate's\Nfault you can't eat choco-mint,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you cowards are always\Nso quick to blame the mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coward"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then these jerks always go to\N"No way can that be good"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Why don't you just eat toothpaste, then?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Morons{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toothpaste isn't something you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you even imagine it, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How humiliating it is to be mocked\Nby idiots who don't know the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between toothpaste and {\i1}food{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I {\i1}really {\i0}can't stand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the sheer {\i1}arrogance {\i0}of people\Nwho think it's okay to persecute
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what they don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We choco-mintians\Nhave been exposed for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Choco-mintians"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exposed to the unknowing abuse\Nthat stems from a lack of understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just toothpaste?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When choco-mint, as ice cream,\Nmade its way to Japan from distant continents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sales were poor due to its\Nintense coloration and unique flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We choco-mintians, amidst bias and prejudice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,slowly grew in number with many years of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's praised as\Ninvigorating, Instagrammable--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with more cafés serving choco-mint sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and more varieties of choco-mint goods\Non food-store shelves every year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nevertheless{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palate-poor anti-choco-mint\Nbrigade chooses ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise, O choco-mintians!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn your sadness into anger\Nand make your stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate it, don't you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks when people mock your favorite game\Nwhen they've never played it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and know nothing about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's all out of order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mint doesn't taste like toothpaste--\N{\i1}toothpaste {\i0}tastes like {\i1}mint{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idiot{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She... She is {\i1}seriously {\i0}pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind those palate-poor losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for choco-mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, choco-mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bite and the sharp,\Nrefreshing mint flavor fills your mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the gentle notes of sweet chocolate\Nslowly fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That soothing feeling makes you\Nwant to take another bite right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...choco-mint is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brava. I guess you've been\Nholding onto some things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}yeah{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hate whatever you want,\Nbut don't diss what someone else likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own beeswax!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you {\i1}did {\i0}mock my solo movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, I never dreamed that {\i1}you{\i0}\Nwould be one of those lower lifeforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over one lousy ice cream? That's a little much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I {\i1}hate {\i0}it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't handle mint as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, anything with that cooling\Nsensation--gum, cough drops--forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even use a non-mint toothpaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cooling sensation is the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the sweet chocolate chaser?\NThat's the real charm of choco-mint!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I can't do mint,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never tried choco-mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... Mock choco-mint untasted, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So it all stems from childhood trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means you should be fine now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do say your sense of\Ntaste changes as you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna try one, just to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hesitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine--it's not an intense mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conquer your pickiness. Mint's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just eat it already. C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine. Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An indirect--?!\NWait--now it's rubbing off on {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't eat this now,\Nit'll turn into this big thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't she be a little more mindful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... it's actually, uh... tasty, I... I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty vague answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you managed to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last one's mine!
